channel.title: Cheddr - Pittsburgh (Matik Remix)
channel.description:
Hi! This is a track that I remixed for @Cheddr's song Pittsburgh.
You can check out the original here: https://soundcloud.com/cheddr/pittsburgh
This track was released a couple weeks back, but I was requested just recently that I should post it on the forum! I guess you say this track is future? It has some elements of it in there, but I'm still not entirely sure. There's also a completely different genre that changes during the end! About three-quarters of the time, I was being lazy and not working on it, so it kind of took me a while to get out to the public.
Anyways, for those who haven't listened, here it is:
https://soundcloud.com/matikauxy/cheddr-pittsburgh-matik-remix
![50%20pm|500x500](upload://31OUvMOjqUQUkjEX2vdIiQoWxaQ.jpg)
